editorialNotes.standard: We love the chaotic whimsy of cute animals launching lightning strikes and sawblades to seize the lead in this auto-running racer.

Weâ€™re blown away by the newest installment of EAâ€™s popular racing franchise. We found ourselves gawking at reflections, lens flare, and scenery as we motored through hairpin turns at breakneck speeds. The improvements aren't just cosmetic, thoughâ€”you'll find yourself stunned by the believable roars of engines and the huge variety of true-to-life cars and courses.
